articles.title: 6N: Scotland fights back to beat France 32-26
articles.description: EDINBURGH, Scotland (AP)  Scotland rebounded from its mauling in Wales by fighting back to beat France 32-26 in Six Nations rugby at Murrayfield, with a string of successful penalty kicks by recalled scrumhalf Greig Laidlaw completing the turnaround on Sunday.
